<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" for="text/css">
	<title>Document</title>
</head>
<h1>Mystery Word</h1>



<body>

	<p>Directions: You'll have 8 guesses to correctly guess the Mystery Word. Input your guess in the box below.</p>
	<p class="randomWord">
		{{#blankSpaces}}{{.}}{{/blankSpaces}}</p>
	<p>{{errorMsg}}</p>
	<form action="/" method="post" class="guessInput">
		<input type="text" name="guess" placeholder="Type your guess here!">
		<input type="submit" value="Good Luck!">
		<p>Guessed letter: {{#incorrectGuesses}}{{.}}{{/incorrectGuesses}}</p>
		<p>You have {{guessCount}} guesses left!</p>

	</form>
</body>

</html>